text: you asked for a suggestion for food? If you ever visit Oranda, then try a 'kroket' (croquette) with mustard from the Febo. It's deep-fried fastfood and can be purchased in a kind of vending machine (not available everywhere in Oranda) or just at the counter. And while you eat your kroket, also buy a 'patatje oorlog' (literally: war-fries). That is a portion of fries with mayonnaise, satay-sauce and chopped onions.
